sentences: Derek Sheen is a stand-up comedian from Seattle.
He played music professionally for 15 years before returning to standup at age 35.
He was a headliner at the Akumal Comedy Festival in Mexico.
He appeared on the second season of the Seeso streaming series The Guest List in 2017.
From 2011 to 2014, he co-hosted the podcast Delicious Mediocrity with fellow Seattle comic Douglas Gale.
"Sheen's newest album, Macho Caballero, was released April 24, 2020, on Stand Up!
